						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of 90 sheep for a lamp by a lady by name Nayaṉavalli, wife of one Kalikēsari, son of Kāraikkāḍuḍaiyār. Another 8 sheep was also presented by her for a lamp (being burnt on a special day every month)</p>						

